disdain for wealthy Moscow. Police arrested 79 people in St Petersburg as well as 13 in Rostov-na-Donu and two each in the sleepy towns of Bryansk and Syktyvkar"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:15:17.000Z","msg":"俄國差佬個人資料公開貼連登，黑警資料公開貼俄國Forum，咁樣合作得唔得？"},{"pid":"707689958a729cde571698d4bd1a94160c913a06","tid":1453441,"uid":21963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:18:07.000Z","msg":"做乜撚有個中二病癲婆係到鳩嗡"},{"pid":"54bbeef08f27d751e6b49e920d8fd9e01bdf1e35","tid":1453441,"uid":210254,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:19:07.000Z","msg":"諗得過<br />\n留名夜啲search下你講嘅資料"},{"pid":"65c438934acfd3f13475ade3d392613f91001bf0","tid":1453441,"uid":208373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:19:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ffeeee3ec1073b9c42525a7a434a144e5154fe5c","tid":1453441,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:21:32.000Z","msg":"感謝!!!<br />\n<br />\n就來變世界大戰!<br />\n<br />\n也懇請大家一起支持 &amp; 加入這個方向:<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">海外文宣: 請求中立醫療船支援香港平民</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1446851/page/7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1446851/page/7</a>"},{"pid":"667e1e129e2f7c91ae496c31e459d4fd435e3c4c","tid":1453441,"uid":274658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:22:24.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯都應該係睇到香港有先會出嚟<br />\n我覺得可以傳啲火俾俄羅斯兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等上面仲想搞我地丫嗱"},{"pid":"8ff929a077ec89579884dc7f711a32bb53bef426","tid":1453441,"uid":296222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:23:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c4b9c391b21751e42b058e6d4083b18e44b2239","tid":1453441,"uid":221342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:24:08.000Z","msg":"其實要聲援，同敵人，同陣線，同處境"},{"pid":"c9a9e81be0d6a1ab